      "updated": 1700000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Claude calls tools iteratively  (agentic loop)\n\n  get_market_data()          →  price, candles (6 timeframes)\n  get_portfolio_state()      →  balance, open positions, P&L\n  analyze_news_sentiment()   →  EmotionScore from Claude\n  get_technical_indicators() →  RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, trend",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Claude calls tools iteratively  (agentic loop)\n\n  get_market_data()          →  price, candles (6 timeframes)\n  get_portfolio_state()      →  balance, open positions, P&L\n  analyze_news_sentiment()   →  EmotionScore from Claude\n  get_technical_indicators() →  RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, trend"
    },
